  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-gray-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">🌍 About Me</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      Hello 👋, I’m <strong>Muhayat</strong>, a Lecturer in Information Technology. 
      I believe that technology should <em>empower, not deceive</em>.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      This website is dedicated to sharing:
    </p>
