      <li>📚 <strong>Course Materials</strong> – interactive learning guides for IT students.</li>
      <li>✍️ <strong>Articles & Insights</strong> – technology trends, digital security, and practical tips.</li>
      <li>💡 <strong>Quote of The Day (QOTD)</strong> – daily inspiration for academic and digital careers.</li>
      <li>🚀 <strong>Tech Inspirations</strong> – creative ideas and stories to grow together.</li>
